title: Serena Garcia de Vera’s 15th Birthday picnic
content:
Milliken Park, Scarborough, Aug. 29, 2015 
 
SERENA celebrates her 15th birthday with friends and family — all four generations of them — with lots of food and games for all ages. The celebrant is the daughter of Kalayaan Garcia de Vera and Derek de Vera. 
 
Birthday girl cuts her cake, with friends and cousins.
